Reclusa:

"Identify indeed.Like I really need any introduction."  She walked
right up to Perceptor and stared into his optics. "I am not one to
take orders. But, so you know who I am, I am Reclusa. Decendant of
Black Arachnia. Soon to be avenger of my ancestors killers. Now." She
pressed her tiny finger on his chest, "You identify yourself to me."

OOC: (Bold little thing isn't she?)
